MODIFICATIONS UNDER APACHE 2.0 § 4(b):
The Gemma 4 E2B weights have been losslessly re-encoded from fp16 to a
4-tier GF(17) RGBA pixel atlas representation (the "Reffelt decomposition").
Cosine similarity of the round-tripped weights against the original fp16
weights is 1.0 (bit-exact reversible). No fine-tuning, distillation, or
lossy compression has been applied. The transformation is purely a storage
format conversion.

